CBRE are proud to present to the market for sale or lease, 28-30 Miller Street, Murarrie. This prime freestander is situated within the heart of Murarrie, which remains one of Brisbane's most sought after industrial hubs in South-East Queensland. Murarrie is approximately 9 kilometres south east of the Brisbane CBD and enjoys primary access to major arterial routes through the Gateway Motorway interchange.

The property is improved with a modern, 1,389sqm* freestanding building. Some of the main features of this property include:

• 777sqm* of highbay, clearspan warehouse
• 612sqm* of corporate office space split over two levels
• Situated on 1,879sqm* regular shaped allotment
• Warehouse is accessed via 2 electric roller doors
• Provides excellent street frontage along with exposure to Creek Road
• Fully fenced and secured site
• Excellent location providing easy access to major arterials

*Approx

For further information or to arrange your inspection, please don't hesitate to contact Exclusive Agent Ben
Lyons from CBRE.

Approx*

Murarrie is approx. 7 radial kilometres from the Brisbane CBD, 8 radial Kilometres from Brisbane Airport and approx. 10 radial kilometres from the Port of Brisbane.

Positioned within Metroplex Business Park Estate, 7.5 radial kilometres east of the Brisbane CBD and located within close proximity to the Gateway and Port of Brisbane Motorway - its location is highly sought after.

- 500sqm* corporate grade office with prominent corner exposure. 
- 7,010sqm* high clearance fully sprinklered warehouse

For further information or to arrange your inspection please contact Exclusive Agents from CBRE or Colliers listed below.

This complex is well positioned approx. 8 radial kilometres south-east of the Brisbane CBD and provides excellent access to the Airport, Port of Brisbane and Gateway Motorway.

This concrete, tilt panel office/warehouse boasts many features such as corporate appeal, high quality office fit-out and 54sqm of secure, concrete hardstand at the rear of the unit. The warehouse is clear span and has an 80sqm* mezzanine at the rear of the unit providing additional storage or offers the ability to extend the upstairs office. Some of the feature of this property are:

- Open plan office space with a boardroom and small office on first level
- 80sqm* mezzanine for extra storage or office expansion
- Fully fenced and secured 54sqm* concrete hardstand at rear accessed via roller door
- Clear span warehouse
- 3-phase power
- Amenities on both levels
- Corporate looking facade with street frontage 

For further information regarding this outstanding opportunity or should you wish to arrange an inspection, please contact Agents Ben Lyons or Braiden Farrer of CBRE today.
